latestIgtvVideos.title: Jester Red Kurta Set
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
This rich but casual ensemble is a must for your next party as it brings a deep plum red and midnight blue together with delicate gold designs. The deep red kurta top is embroidered with a simple and bold geometrical gold pattern that matches with the patterns on the cuff sleeves. The dark blue wide set palazzo pants contrast beautifully with the deep red top and feature a simple gold striped border to match. With colours that seem to be a match made in heaven, you’re sure to be the showstopper at the next event you go to decked up in this outfit!

Fabric : Cotton
